<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Document déjà signé</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f8f5ff; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 1rem; }
  .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 2.5rem 2rem; max-width: 440px; width: 100%; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08); text-align: center; }
  .icon { font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.3rem; color: #1a1a2e; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
  p { color: #666; font-size: .9rem; line-height: 1.6; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
  <div class="icon">📝</div>
  <h1>Document déjà signé</h1>
  <p>La facture <strong>{{ invoice.number }}</strong> a déjà été signée le {{ invoice.signedAt|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}.<br>Ce lien n'est plus utilisable.</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
